Overview

Jim Is Here For You is an open-source framework for running a persistent, autonomous X account that:

Observes tweets on your timeline

Decides when to reply

Decides how to reply

Posts unprompted thoughts

Remembers past interactions

Gradually becomes more unhinged (by design)

Jim is:

Schizo-coded

Brainrotted

Chronically online

Jim is not general-purpose.
Jim does not deploy tokens.
Jim does not manage tasks.

Jim posts.

What Jim Does (Exactly)

At runtime, Jim runs a loop:

Reads recent tweets (timeline, mentions, or searches)

Checks internal state (energy, mood, rot level)

Decides whether to:

Reply

Quote

Post independently

Stay silent and observe

Generates text using its configured LLM

Posts to X

Logs the interaction into memory

Thinks about what just happened

Repeats

This loop never â€œfinishes.â€

